title: [Valtina's General Store]
[Valtina's Outfitting]
[Valtina's Armory]
description: Refined oak-paneled walls rise from a varnished dark oak floor.  Just above a woven Vornavian silk rug hangs a trio-bladed mounted vellum fan, and a dark and light oak ceiling completes the picture.  A Vornavian silk-lined display case stands in the middle of the room.
